# Python Changes â†’ Rebuild

Editing any `.py` file means:

1. Run linters:
   ```bash
   npm run lint:python:fix
   npm run format:python
   npm run lint
   ```
2. Rebuild add-on:
   ```bash
   cd cync-controller && ./rebuild.sh
   # or: ha addons rebuild local_cync-controller
   ```
3. Tail logs to confirm:
   ```bash
   ha addons logs local_cync-controller --follow
   ```

Restarting alone will not load Python changes.
